Class TransactionFileListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist.io.TransactionFileListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileAlterationListener

    final class TransactionFileListener
extends Observable
implements FileAlterationListener
    This FileAlterationListener implementation is notified about relevant modifications in the file system. It propagates these modifications to its Observers.
    Author:
    Florian J. Breunig
